  "remarks": "\nNIRU BATTERY MANUFACTURING COMPANY is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. NIRU BATTERY MANUFACTURING COMPANY is owned or controlled directly or indirectly by a person who is or has been so involved, namely the Ministry of Defence Armed Forces Logistics (MODAFL).",
